Dependency Injection:
    FiatEngine{

    }

    class Car{
      FiatEngine engine;
    }
    In the above example the fiatEngine depends on car class and that we call as dependency and The injection is nothing
    but creating instance for the fiat Engine class.

We will be having
   - Xml based configuration. - This we are not going to use and dont use it anywhere in your projects
   - Annotation based Configuration
   - Java based configuration
